                                    "detail": 0,
                                    "format": 0,
                                    "mode": "normal",
                                    "style": "",
                                    "text": " bottle design. I took the bottle from sketches from Laazy Studio's design team to a precision CAD model that served as the final production file for the manufacturer. A long the way I used Blender to produce high fidelity renderings of different design options for client approval. Lastly I developed a web integration with Three JS that let the model be displayed in real time 3D on Isolation Proof's website.",
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "version": 1
