                        {
                            "children": [
                                {
                                    "detail": 0,
                                    "format": 0,
                                    "mode": "normal",
                                    "style": "",
                                    "text": "These early sketches provided by Laazy Studio outlined the basic shape of the bottle, embossed details, and the labels that would adorn it. I used Rhino to create a model of the glass based on these sketches and brought it into Blender to quickly add the embossed details and labels. I then setup a simple environment and rendered a visualization of the design for client approval.     ",
                                    "type": "text",
                                    "version": 1
                                }
